            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">左派的抱怨</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="261944828">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-261944828" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-261944828" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="261944828">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3486579/">shumi2</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-04-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这是一本写于40年前的悲愤之作，今日的世界各国的经济关系已大不相同；理智的知识分子会把目光更多地投注于国内因素剖析。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
